data.description:
Beautiful Custom Ranch Home nestled on a Gorgeous 1 Acre Private Rural site boasting Lovely Views of Bald Mountain & the Front Range. This Home provides 3 Bedrooms, 3 Baths, Attached 2 Car Garage & a Detached 2 Car Garage with a Workshop.  Welcome home to a Covered Front Porch & inside  to a Vaulted Foyer with Beautiful Wood Flooring that flows throughout the Main Level. The Great Room showcases Soaring Ceilings & a Gas Fireplace with a Mantel & Hearth, perfect for those chilly evenings. Your intimate Dining Room is Bright with a 2 story window & is the ideal space for entertaining Guests. The Kitchen is a Chef's delight offering multiple work spaces on Quartz Counters, Stainless Steel appliances, lots of storage in the Bright White Cabinetry, Breakfast Bar Seating & Glass French doors with access to an Expansive Covered Composite Deck. Or step down to the large Flagstone Patio. Both are perfect for Relaxing and Entertaining with scenic Vistas of your Wooded Backyard & the Mountains. Main Level includes a Quiet Front Office with a Closet (could be a 4th Bedroom with the addition of French Doors) and a Spacious Primary Suite finished with a custom Walk-in Closet and French Doors offering Lovely Views that lead out to the Deck. The Lavish Primary 4-Piece Bath is sure to impress with its attractive Walk-in Shower, Tiling, Double Quartz Vanities and a Water Closet. 

There are 2 more Bedrooms, one non-conforming. Currently used as a Library, it could easily be converted to a conforming bed with the addition of a closet. There's also a Full Bath, Powder Room, and a Laundry/Mud Room that has Garage access and is finished with Cabinetry, Counter space and a Linen Closet. Great additional Living Space and Mountain Views in the sizable upstairs Family/Bonus Room. Large amount of Storage capacity in the "stand up" Crawl Space which also houses the mechanicals.

There are 2 Oversized Garages. One is Attached, has 592 SqFt with Storage Space, an Exterior Access Door, Windows and Concrete Pad. The Detached Garage/Workshop is 24' x 30'(720 SqFt) and  can accommodate 1-2 vehicles depending on size. The Garage/Workshop is Drywalled and has Built-in Cabinets, Counters, Lighting, Heating and an Exterior Access Door. The Storage/Garden Shed, built in 2021, is 14' x 16'. Lots of off-street Parking on the Paved Driveway for your Guests. Also great for parking your RV, Trailer or Boat. 

Additional Amenities of this Private Rural home with Stucco include Landscaping, Stone and Cement Walkways. Enjoy a mixture of majestic Ponderosa Pines and Gamble Oak. Private Well does allow for irrigation. Nicely located across from large Wooded Acreage sites. Quick Easy access to I-25. Close to Shopping, Dining  and Retail in Monument and just a couple miles to Golf.
